data.description: Well maintained tri-level two-family home is very spacious featuring two bedrooms and one bath on the 1st-floor apartment. Second floor two bedrooms one full bath, third floor 1 bedroom full bath. Although it does not have a basement (it's a crawl space) the full third floor has plenty of usable and livable space. There are also two assigned spaces for parking that come with the home. Large backyard on 20x144 lot accessed via the second floor. This is a large home with almost 3000sq feet of living space.
